{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 30}Therefore say to the house of Israel, \uc1\u8217*Thus saith Jehovah: "Do ye defile yourselves after the manner of your fathers, play the harlot after their abominations,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 31}and defile yourselves with all your idols by offering your gifts, by making your sons to pass through the fire, even to this day? and shall I be consulted by you, O house of Israel?  As I live," saith Jehovah, "I will not be consulted by you;{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 32}and that which cometh into your mind shall not be, in that ye say, We will be as the nations, as the families of the lands, to serve wood and stone."\uc1\u8217*
