{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
 The cup of thy sister Samaria,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 34}thou shalt drink it and drain it, 
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
 Thou shalt break it into fragments, thou shalt tear thy breasts, 
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
 For I myself have spoken, is the oracle of Jehovah. 
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
 Because thou hast forgotten me and cast me aside, 
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
 Therefore thou also shalt bear thy lewdness and thy harlotries.
\par}

{\pard
\par}
{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 36}And Jehovah said to me: Son of man, wilt thou judge Oholah and Oholi- bah? Then show them their abominations,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 37}for they have committed adultery and blood is on their hands; also with their idols have they com- mitted adultery, and their own sons, whom they bore to me, they have turned over to them to be devoured by fire.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 38}This also they have done to me: they have profaned my sanctuaries\uc1\u8217* and defiled my sabbaths,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 39}for when they sacri- ficed their sons to their idols they entered my sanctuary on the same day to pollute it. Behold, thus they have done, within my house.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 40}And moreover they sent for men who came from afar, to whom the messengers were sent; and behold, they came, for whom thou didst bathe and paint thine eyes, and deck thyself with ornaments,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 41}and didst sit on the beautiful divan, with table spread before it, and upon it thou didst put mine incense and mine oil,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 42}and there was the sound of a joyful melody. They also sent for men of the common type, drunkards, brought in from the wilderness, and they put bracelets upon their hands and splendid crowns upon their heads.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 44}Men went* in unto them as one goes in to a harlot; so they went in unto Oholah and Oholibah, to commit lewdness,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 45}but righteous men shall pronounce upon them the judgment of adulteresses, for they are adulteresses, and blood is on their hands!
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 46}Thus saith Jehovah: Bring up a host against them, and give them over to violence and plunder,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 47}let them be stoned with stones, and cut down with swords, let their sons and their daughters, and their houses be burned with fire.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 48}Thus will I cause lewdness to cease in the land, and all women shall be instructed, and will not imitate your lewdness.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 49}I will requite you for your lewdness. Ye shall bear the sins of your idols, and ye shall know that I am the Lord Jehovah.
