{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24 
{\cf1\f1\fs22 24}Again in the tenth month of the ninth year, in the tenth day of the month, this word of Jehovah came to me:{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}Son of man, write down the name of this day; on this very day the king of Babylon began to lay siege to Jerusalem.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}And speak a parable to the rebellious house and say to them,
