{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
 Thus saith Jehovah,
\par}

{\pard
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
 \uc1\u8217*Set on the caldron, set it on, also pour water into it, 
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}Put the pieces into it, every good piece, thigh and shoulder; 
