{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
 Fill it with choice bones,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}take of the best of the flock; 
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
 Also kindle wood under it, make it boil vigorously. 
