{\cf1\f1\fs22 35}Moreover this word of Jehovah came to me:{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}Son of man, turn thy face against Mount Seir, and prophesy against it,{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}and say to it, \uc1\u8217*Thus saith the Lord Jehovah:
